IMAPAccount bestmx
Host mail.bestmx.net
UserCmd "pass mail/bestmx.net | awk 'NR == 2 { print $2 }'"
PassCmd "pass mail/bestmx.net | awk 'NR == 1'"
SSLType STARTTLS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2

IMAPStore bestmx-remote
Account bestmx

MaildirStore bestmx-local
Path ~/Maildir/bestmx/
Inbox ~/Maildir/bestmx/INBOX/
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel bestmx
Far :bestmx-remote:
Near :bestmx-local:
Pattern * !"Archive"
Create Near
Remove Near
Expunge Both
SyncState *
CopyArrivalDate yes


IMAPAccount intabs
Host intabs.net
UserCmd "pass mail/intabs.net | awk 'NR == 2 { print $2 }'"
PassCmd "pass mail/intabs.net | awk 'NR == 1'"
SSLType STARTTLS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2

IMAPStore intabs-remote
Account intabs

MaildirStore intabs-local
Path ~/Maildir/intabs/
Inbox ~/Maildir/intabs/INBOX/
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel intabs
Far :intabs-remote:
Near :intabs-local:
Pattern * !"Archive"
Create Near
Remove Near
Expunge Both
SyncState *
CopyArrivalDate yes
